This paper deals with natural language processing and machine learning techniques to detect and classify norm conflicts in contracts. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CL (Computation and Language). The paper also involves the use of deep learning models, which suggests that it could belong to cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.LG (Machine Learning). Additionally, the paper deals with security and privacy issues related to contracts, which could place it in cs.CR (Cryptography and Security) and cs.IR (Information Retrieval).
